      "span_text": "Although it was first though that 10% of the genome is under circadian control [CITATION_1] , recent studies on mouse tissues indicate that roughly 50% of all genes oscillate in a circadian manner [CITATION_2] , reinforcing the idea of a tissue-specific regulation."
